text: Dillinger is a 1945 American crime drama movie directed by Max Nosseck and starring Lawrence Tierney in the title role, Edmund Lowe, Anne Jeffreys, Eduardo Cianelli, Marc Lawrence, Elisha Cook Jr.. It was nominated for an Academy Award in 1946 and was distributed by Monogram Pictures. ==Other websites== * * Category:1945 drama movies Category:1945 crime movies Category:1940s biographical movies Category:1940s crime drama movies Category:American biographical movies Category:1940s American crime drama movies Category:Movies directed by Max Nosseck Category:Movies set in Indiana
